  "summaries": [
    "<b>Luminite</b> is a <linked>Hardmode</linked> <linked>ore</linked> dropped exclusively by the <linked>Moon Lord</linked> in stacks of 70–90 (<linked>90–110</linked>). It can be used to craft <linked>Luminite Bars</linked>, which can then be used to craft several end-game items, like the <linked>Solar</linked>, <linked>Nebula</linked>, <linked>Vortex</linked>, and <linked>Stardust</linked> <linked>tools</linked> and <linked>armor</linked>.",
    "Crafting all items (excluding ammunition) requires a total of 317 Luminite Bars (1,268 Luminite; requires defeating the Moon Lord 15–19 / <linked>12–15</linked> times). Crafting all items pertaining to one type of <linked>Lunar Fragment</linked> (i.e., armor, wings, pickaxe, and hamaxe) requires 68 Luminite Bars (204 Luminite) in addition to 85 of the Lunar Fragment; this requires defeating the Moon Lord only 3 / <linked>2-3</linked> times."
